    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Fuinjutsu (Advanced Seal)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 7</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 6</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 21 | <b>Successes:</b> 3</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 9 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 22</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, F, S</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You touch the target with an advanced seal, which sticks to them until the duration expires or until they fall below 0 HP and are dying, at which point the seal immediately stabilizes the target. Once the seal triggers or its duration expires, it becomes a blank piece of paper and falls off.</p>\n\n\n\n",
